          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "In this exercise, you will use the Codebeamer Library to copy tracker items from another project into your working project. The library provides a drag-and-drop interface for reusing items across projects, and automatically creates a <strong>copy of</strong> association linking the new item back to its original source."
