                  "action": "Optionally, edit the association's Propagate Suspects setting to control whether changes to the original item will flag your copy as suspected.",
                  "detail": "When Propagate Suspects is enabled, changes to the original item cause a suspected badge on your copy. This is useful when you want to stay aware of changes to the source material.",
                  "hint": "Click the edit icon on the association to access the Propagate Suspects toggle."
